item.title: Rate my accounts
item.dc:creator: @xxlegitxx xxlegitxx
item.description:
@xxlegitxx wrote:

exe626:

I can achieve 99 fletching in 2 weeks(even if I only play 2 hours a day).

It takes 76234 bows cut and strung (and 148 bronze arrows) to get to level 99 from 0 exp.
2 weeks (2 hours a day) = 28 hours = 1680 minutes = 100800 seconds.

You would have to string one bow every 1.32 seconds to achieve that. I’m skeptical. And I’m generous in not including the 148 bronze arrows and time spent getting materials (it would cost over 60 mill just to go from 85 thru 99; I doubt you have 60 mil sitting there), by assuming you have it all ready and you are only hardcore fletching.
